    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>For The Crown – The Addictive Puzzle-Building Game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 <strong>Winner of &quot;Best Game Programming Project SAE 2023&quot;</strong> (See the award on YouTube)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build production chains, optimize resource flows, and grow your empire! <strong>For The Crown</strong> is a <strong>puzzle-building game</strong> where every decision matters. Connect buildings, fine-tune your economy, and <strong>turn simple resources into gold</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💡 <strong>Why you won’t be able to stop playing:</strong><br>✔️ <strong>Easy to pick up, fun to master</strong> – Place buildings &amp; paths in seconds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191410/extras/af526667259db072358ba58ceeb72ba9.poster.avif?t=1738754571\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191410/extras/af526667259db072358ba58ceeb72ba9.webm?t=1738754571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191410/extras/af526667259db072358ba58ceeb72ba9.mp4?t=1738754571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Deep production chains</strong> – Watch your economy come to life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191410/extras/fc343f6e80e9d5a99bb0aa167b1bff40.poster.avif?t=1738754571\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191410/extras/fc343f6e80e9d5a99bb0aa167b1bff40.webm?t=1738754571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191410/extras/fc343f6e80e9d5a99bb0aa167b1bff40.mp4?t=1738754571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Exponential complexity</strong> – Your creations evolve into massive networks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191410/extras/399ae302ff2e6442cc3ea7fda331c603.poster.avif?t=1738754571\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191410/extras/399ae302ff2e6442cc3ea7fda331c603.webm?t=1738754571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191410/extras/399ae302ff2e6442cc3ea7fda331c603.mp4?t=1738754571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>4 Tiers</strong> – Every tier has unique buildings and production chains.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>50 handcrafted levels</strong> – Quick 30-minute challenges to deep 6-hour puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Dynamic difficulty</strong> – More frequent rewards, better game flow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>No waiting – just pure strategy</strong> – No idle mechanics, just smart planning and satisfying progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you build the perfect production chain and <strong>claim the crown?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👑 <strong>Play now and become a master of optimization!</strong></p>",
